_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"region_pending\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著异常，p99变化率分别达到1.8152和1.6106，表明支付服务响应时间严重恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-2的rrt_max从正常中位数1807ms上升到故障中位数2032ms，p99从3065.96ms飙升到63312.56ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标异常，p99变化率1.5691，表明物流服务响应时间显著恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-1的rrt_max从2054ms上升到2233ms，p99从6998.04ms飙升到57959.36ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标异常，p99变化率1.5291，表明邮件服务响应时间显著恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"emailservice-1的rrt_max从3168ms上升到3361ms，p99从8115.78ms飙升到60818.02ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"region_pending指标异常，中位数变化率0.3244，表明TiDB存储层存在区域处理积压问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tikv的region_pending从正常中位数7782上升到故障中位数10795，可能存在数据库性能瓶颈\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate的p99变化率1.0163，表明节点CPU使用率峰值异常升高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"aiops-k8s-08节点的node_cpu_usage_rate的p99从25.0%上升到76.65%，可能存在资源竞争问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的链路追踪数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **延迟指标 (`rrt_max`)**:\n   - `frontend->frontend`: `hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies` 延迟从 2864.12ms 增加到 183446.61ms (64倍)。\n   - `frontend->frontend`: `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 延迟从 11203.64ms 增加到 106526.60ms (9.5倍)。\n   - `checkoutservice->checkoutservice`: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote` 延迟从 9347.60ms 增加到 48597.30ms (5.2倍)。\n   - `cartservice->cartservice`: `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 延迟从 2462.71ms 增加到 141488.45ms (57.5倍)。\n\n2. **错误状态 (`error_ratio`)**:\n   - `frontend` 服务在 `hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.` 操作中返回了 HTTP 500 错误。\n\n3. **调用关系**:\n   - `frontend->frontend`: 多个内部调用出现显著延迟。\n   - `checkoutservice->shippingservice`: 延迟增加。\n   - `cartservice->cartservice`: 延迟显著增加。\n\n### 假设与证据\n1. **根因组件**: `frontend` 服务\n   - **原因**: `error_ratio` 增加 (HTTP 500 错误) 和 `rrt_max` 显著增加。\n   - **证据**: `frontend` 服务的多个内部调用出现高延迟和错误。\n\n2. **根因组件**: `cartservice` 服务\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 显著增加。\n   - **证据**: `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 延迟增加了 57.5 倍。\n\n3. **根因组件**: `checkoutservice` 服务\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 增加。\n   - **证据**: `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote` 延迟增加了 5.2 倍。\n\n### 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"cartservice->cartservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HTTP status code: 500\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies 延迟从 2864.12ms 增加到 183446.61ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart 延迟从 2462.71ms 增加到 141488.45ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote 延迟从 9347.60ms 增加到 48597.30ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
